== 續集 ==
''搖滾夏令營"的續集正在計劃中。迪士尼表示續集正在醞釀之中，不過要取決於Jonas Brothers和[[黛咪·洛瓦特|黛咪·洛瓦特]]的繁忙檔期。<ref name="Sequel">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ib3b4f691bfdc20777e32639ff64db485 |author=Kimberly Nordyke |date=2008-06-24 |accessdate=2008-06-24 |title='Camp Rock' sequel in the works |publisher=Hollywood Reporter |archive-date=2008-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080626042009/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/news/e3ib3b4f691bfdc20777e32639ff64db485 |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 新角色的試鏡己於八月開始，電影將會在Haliburton的Wanakita營地，Minden的Kilcoo，Ontario營地拍攝。Ontario營地正是第一部電影的拍攝地。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://glambamm.com/20/camp-rock-2/ |author= |date=2008-06-19 |accessdate=2008-06-25 |title=Camp Rock 2 |publisher=Glam Bamm |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109001036/http://glambamm.com/20/camp-rock-2/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref> The cast are expected to begin filming again in late spring or summer 2009.<ref name="Sequel"/> 

 Disney Channel World的總裁[[:en:Gary_Marsh|Gary Marsh]]，在''紐約日報'' 中證實戲組已經在寫《搖滾夏令營 2》的戲本。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://chattahbox.com/entertainment/2008/06/17/disney-already-planning-sequel-to-camp-rock/ |author= |date=2008-06-17 |accessdate=2008-06-22 |title=Disney Already Planning Sequel to Camp Rock |publisher=Chattahbox |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080912192451/http://chattahbox.com/entertainment/2008/06/17/disney-already-planning-sequel-to-camp-rock/ |archive-date=2008-09-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

Acting Info blog的發表者Alan Baltes表示《搖滾夏令營 2》已暫定於2009年6月7日首播。因為《搖滾夏令營》已經播出，因此《搖滾夏令營 2》的前期製作可能需要立刻進行。正式拍攝日期不會在2009年頭開始。 [[黛咪·洛瓦特|黛咪·洛瓦特]]、強納斯三兄弟、 Meaghan Jette Martin、艾莉森·斯通勒、Anna Maria Perez de Tagle、Jasmine Richards、Maria Canals Barrera、Jordan Francis和Aaryn Doyle都會演出《搖滾夏令營 2》；而Daniel Fathers、Julie Brown和 Roshon Fegan 暫時未被列入戲組之中。

根據[[:en:The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]，所有主要演員均希望回歸《搖滾夏令營 2》，而戲中會有強納斯家族的小弟─Frankie Jonas作為客串嘉賓。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.24-7pressrelease.com/view_press_release_printer_friendly.php?rID=53712 |author= |date=2008-06-17 |accessdate=2008-06-22 |title=Frankie Jonas to appear in Camp Rock 2 |publisher=24-7 Press Release |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080925213447/http://www.24-7pressrelease.com/view_press_release_printer_friendly.php?rID=53712 |archivedate=2008年9月25日 |df= }}</ref>

